Main problem is that the data source of a `PowerPoint` chart is a embedded `Excel` worksheet. And this worksheet needs changed too additional to the cached data in the chart. That means we need get the chart&#39;s data source which is a Excel sheet. And then we need set all new category data, new series titles and new data values always in that sheet as well as in the chart.

Complete example:

Lets start with that `LineSample.pptx` template:

